#. VAR: 9. Samaṇavagga → vaggāsaṅgahitā suttantā (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.85:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga "
msgstr "9. An Ascetic "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 85. Bhikkhusutta → bhikkhudhammasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.85:0.3"
msgid "85. Bhikkhusutta "
msgstr "85. A Mendicant "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.85:1.1"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ, bhikkhave, dhammānaṃ bhinnattā bhikkhu hoti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, it’s because of breaking seven things that you become a mendicant. "

msgctxt "an7.85:1.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.85:1.3"
msgid "Sakkāyadiṭṭhi bhinnā hoti, vicikicchā bhinnā hoti, sīlabbataparāmāso bhinno hoti, rāgo bhinno hoti, doso bhinno hoti, moho bhinno hoti, māno bhinno hoti. "
msgstr "Identity view, doubt, misapprehension of precepts and observances, greed, hate, delusion, and conceit. "

msgctxt "an7.85:1.4"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sattannaṃ dhammānaṃ bhinnattā bhikkhu hotī”ti. "
msgstr "It’s because of breaking these seven things that you become a mendicant.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.85:1.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

